info: Mathematics is an area of knowledge that includes such topics as numbers, formulas and related structures.
English is a West Germanic language of the Indo-European language family, with its earliest forms spoken by the inhabitants of early medieval England.
Physics is the natural science that studies matter, its fundamental constituents, its motion and behavior through space and time.
Chemistry is the scientific study of the properties and behavior of matter. It is a natural science that covers the elements that make up matter to the compounds composed of atoms.
Biology is the scientific study of life. It is a natural science with a broad scope but has several unifying themes that tie it together as a single, coherent field.
History is an American pay television network and flagship channel owned by A&E Networks.
Economics is the social science that studies the production, distribution, and consumption of goods and services.
